# 10. Create setup directories

```text
Create iOSiSH setup directories?

Recommended directories:
- /var/lib/iosish
- /var/lib/iosish/state
- /var/lib/iosish/logs
- /etc/iosish
- /usr/local/lib/iosish
- /usr/local/bin

1) Yes, recommended
2) Skip and continue
```

Default: `1`

---

# 11. Logging

```text
Enable setup logging?

Logs will be saved to:
/var/lib/iosish/logs/install.log

1) Yes, recommended
2) Skip and continue
```

Default: `1`

