# 12. Save preflight state

```text
Save preflight results for later modules?

This lets the TUI know:
- which packages are installed
- whether network works
- whether certificates are ready
- whether apk repositories look correct

1) Yes, recommended
2) Skip and continue
```

Default: `1`

