# Recommended preflight package sets

## Minimal baseline

```sh
ca-certificates curl wget git openssh-client less nano
```

## Recommended baseline

```sh
ca-certificates curl wget git openssh-client less nano bash file grep sed gawk tar xz unzip zip shadow
```

## Extended baseline

```sh
ca-certificates curl wget git openssh-client less nano bash file grep sed gawk tar xz unzip zip shadow util-linux procps ncurses ncurses-terminfo-base
```

## Build baseline

```sh
build-base make gcc musl-dev linux-headers pkgconf
```

---

# Best default flow

```text
1) apk update
2) apk upgrade
3) install ca-certificates
4) update-ca-certificates
5) install recommended baseline packages
6) check network
7) check Alpine branch
8) create setup dirs
9) enable logging
10) write preflight state
```
